cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CYBER, cs.CR 

The paper applies neural networks to model customer online behaviours for digital marketing purposes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with natural language processing. Additionally, the paper involves cybersecurity aspects, which could place it in the cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) category. Finally, since the paper discusses conversion prediction and advertising retargeting, it could also be classified under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
